Tailored analysis tables with baseline patient data.

tailored_patientbl.Rd

Tailored analysis tables with baseline patient data.

Usage

tailored_patientbl(stcs)

Arguments

stcs

A list containing the STCS data frame.

Value

A data frame.

Details

tailored_patientbl(): PK: patientkey.

  • 1. patientkey: Identifier of patients. Source: Patient.

  • 2. patid: STCS Identifier of patients. Source: Patient.

  • 3. enrollment_age: Patient age at enrollment. Source: Patient.

  • 4. sex: Patient sex. Source: Patient.

  • 5. bg: Patient blood group. Source: Patient.

  • 6. istreat: Past IS treatment. Source: Patient.

  • 7. ethnicity: Patient ethnicity. Source: Patient.

  • 8. ethnicity_comment: Comment on patient_ethnicity. Source: Patient.

  • 9. pre_tpx_count: Number of pre-STSC transplantation. Source: Patient.

  • 10. pre_organ_count: Number of pre-STSC organ. Source: Patient.

  • 11. weight: Weight of patient at enrollment. Source: PatientLongitudinal.

  • 12. height: Height of patient at enrollment. Source: PatientLongitudinal.

  • 13. height: Height of patient at enrollment. Source: PatientLongitudinal.

  • 14.-28. hla...: (Optional) Patient HLA. Source: PatientHLA.
